    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning factory finish with a deep, mirror-like gloss and professional ceramic coating. The interior is equally immaculate, featuring supple leather seats with no signs of wear, a pristine dashboard, and that unmistakable new-car scent. Every electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards. With a complete, documented service history and zero mechanical flaws, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example. Not a single stone chip, scratch, or blemish can be found on this masterpiece\u2014it is truly indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
